    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/hvdCategory> <http://data.europa.eu/bna/c_8f0fac04>, <http://data.europa.eu/bna/c_a9135398>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__764.
