    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>, <http://entryscape.com/terms/ServedByDataService>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#105091eb79fec317ff8c26919e9b749b>.
<#105091eb79fec317ff8c26919e9b749b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U17448>;
